rows.label: qst201710_msg0002
rows.name: It seems this is the goal, sir...

rows.label: qst201710_msg0004
rows.name:
Sir, yes, sir! But how do
you know my name, sir?

rows.label: qst201710_msg0005
rows.name:
I have heard the rumors.
That you are an unconventional
but skilled Blade.

rows.label: qst201710_msg0006
rows.name:
Th-Thank you, sir! It is an
honor beyond my station, sir!

rows.label: qst201710_msg0007
rows.name:
Uh, I don't think that
was a compliment.

rows.label: qst201710_msg0008
rows.name:
However, to have the palace's
defenses broken through so easily...

rows.label: qst201710_msg0009
rows.name:
As the ruler of the Empire,
I must admit my feelings
are somewhat complex...

rows.label: qst201710_msg0010
rows.name:
No, Your Majesty, there is
no need to be pessimistic!

rows.label: qst201710_msg0011
rows.name:
The soldiers of Superbia
all fought valliantly!

rows.label: qst201710_msg0013
rows.name:
If you say so, then there
is no doubt it is true.
